{"title":"营长下连","authors":["张立源"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"营长下连"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公安部队某部　张立源"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺们营长下连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀里揣着“老三篇”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问学的咋样？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿！真沾！（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲用会上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他总是第一个发言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮火中摔打这么多年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他却还说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我呀！也得向私心开战！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十来岁的人了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还和俺们一起瞄准，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥臂投弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他却说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“下半辈子革命就得这么干！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺们有了问题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他挂念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看他下连才半月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺们的脾气禀性全摸遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和俺们一起学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和俺们一起谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了把俺们染成鲜红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他翻遍毛主席的书去找答案。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺们说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“营长对俺们真关心。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他却说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“没有你们谁接班！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺们营长下连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活学活用“老三篇”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看营长想自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺们学习有了样板。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：“真沾”河北方言，意思是真行。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}